General Editing

ctl + s = save file
ctl + z = undo
ctl + y = redo
ctl + x = cut
ctl + c = copy file
ctl + v = paste

Navigation

ctl + p = quick open file
ctl + tab = switch between open files
ctl + g = go to line
ctl + shift + e = explorer sidebar
ctl + shift + f = search files
ctl + space = trigger intellisence
ctl + shift + space = trigger parameter hints
alt + up (or) down = move line up/down
alt +shift + up/down = copy line up/down
ctl + / =toggle line comment

Window Management

ctl + shift + n =new Window
ctl + shift + w =close window
ctl + ' = toggle terminal 
ctl + b =toggle sidebar visibility

Debugging 

F5 = start Debugging
F9 = toggle breakpoint
F10 = step over
F11 = step into
shift + F5 =stop Debugging

File Management

ctl + n = create a new file
ctl + shift + t =reopen the last closed file
ctl +  shift + s = save all open files
ctl + o = open file
ctl + w = close the current file
